<title type="html"><![CDATA[12/9 (Thu.) Injuries due to the use of smartphones/10 things you can do to reduce climate change (Host: Joyce)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=569&amp;p=592#p592"><![CDATA[
12/9 (Thu.) Injuries due to the use of smartphones/10 Things you can do to reduce climate change (Host: Joyce)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a hybrid meeting on December 9 (Thursday):<br />On-site meeting:<br />If you have received at least one dose of vaccine, please join our physical meeting: <br />Dante coffee 丹堤 臺北市大安區濟南路三段25號 忠孝新生 MRT Exit 3<br />On-line meeting:<br />If you haven’t gotten any vaccine or live far away from Taipei, please join our online meeting:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br /><br />Session 1<br />Many injuries were reported this year due to the use of smartphones.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4313443">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4313443</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. In a world of increased connectivity, how does social media really affect us?<br />2. Are you really who you portray online?<br />3. How has cell phone changed our lives on a daily basis?<br />4. How can we get rid of our addiction to technology and how can we control the use of our cell phone?<br />5. How and When to Limit Kids' Tech Use?<br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2<br /><br />10 Things You Can Do to Reduce Climate Change<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.publichealth.lacounty.gov/eh/docs/climatechange/ThingYouCanDotoReduceClimateChange.pdf">http://www.publichealth.lacounty.gov/eh ... Change.pdf</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1. What can we do to reduce air pollution at home and city?<br />2. What's the best way to deal with climate change?<br />3. What are the best food that are good for the planet and your health?<br />4. Is a vegetarian diet really more environmentally friendly than eating meat?<br />5. Are vegetarian diets really healthier?<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.丹堤咖啡有100元低消喔!<br />2.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=37037">JuliaHo</a> — Sun Dec 05, 2021 6:17 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
